Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.16,0:01:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,FURFANG FULL ASSAULT
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.59,0:01:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai! Popp! I'm coming with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.47,0:02:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're both disciples of Avan,\Nthen I'm your senior.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.01,0:02:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm going to carry on\NMaster Avan's will and fight, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.60,0:02:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.77,0:02:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.40,0:02:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You can tell me on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.03,0:02:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I think she's going to be\Nbossing us around.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.57,0:02:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That means she's reliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.58,0:02:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.34,0:02:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is! Romos Castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.43,0:02:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Romos Castle here we come!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.69,0:02:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Go home! The king is already asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.32,0:02:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.86,0:02:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh come on! We've come all this way!\NDon't be like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.57,0:03:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but security at the castle\Nhas been increased due to monster attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.33,0:03:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We cannot just allow anyone\Nin the castle at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.83,0:03:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, we happen\Nto know the king personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.63,0:03:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You might get chewed out later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.13,0:03:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep up with the lies\Nand I'll have you thrown in prison!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.38,0:03:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.64,0:03:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! I was sure we'd finally get\Nsome hospitality at the castle tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.73,0:03:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh well. Let's spend tonight in an inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.81,0:03:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. There.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.32,0:03:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome. It's quite late\Nto be out, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.40,0:03:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, the three of us\Nwould like to spend the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.95,0:03:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Just you three?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.49,0:03:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't there any adults?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.74,0:03:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister, we may not look it,\Nbut we're fighting the Dark Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.42,0:03:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You could say we're a Hero's party.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.00,0:04:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.84,0:04:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It just so happens there's another\NHero's party staying here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.97,0:04:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? A Hero?! Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.64,0:04:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,There. They're staying in that room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.14,0:04:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't, Dai! Save it for tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.56,0:04:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh come on! I just want to say hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.86,0:04:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir Hero! Sir Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.44,0:04:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What? It's late.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.57,0:04:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.32,0:04:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.74,0:04:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We're exhausted from\Nbattling monsters all day!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.83,0:04:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't I talk to you a little bit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.25,0:04:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I'll sign an autograph tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.71,0:04:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on? Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.63,0:04:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Some annoying brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.47,0:04:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard that voice before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.05,0:04:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sir Hero! Sir Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.56,0:04:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough! Buzz off!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.18,0:04:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The fake Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.56,0:04:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Th-The monster boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.36,0:04:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.40,0:05:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing in Romos?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.24,0:05:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on, Dai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.82,0:05:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,These guys are villains\Npretending to be Heroes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.24,0:05:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They kidnapped Gomechan\Nand did all sorts of bad stuff!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.79,0:05:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on! We've washed\Nour hands of that stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.09,0:05:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! We paid for our sins\Nand are working to be true Heroes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.34,0:05:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Working by doing what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.60,0:05:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we defeat weaker monsters\Nand get rewards.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.48,0:05:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And open leftover treasure chests\Nat the castles the Dark Army cleared.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.81,0:05:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Coaching soldiers in fighting and magic\Npays pretty well, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.94,0:05:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.20,0:05:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.78,0:05:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's basically what you used to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.87,0:05:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, how can anyone who only fights\Nweaker monsters call themselves a Hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.29,0:06:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You're one to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.25,0:06:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we let bygones be bygones?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.02,0:06:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}From here on, I must be ruthless.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.98,0:06:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The pride and honor of a warrior\Nare meaningless without victory.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.32,0:06:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will use whatever method I can...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.12,0:06:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.02,0:07:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Come out Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.31,0:07:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, Romos Kingdom falls today!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.86,0:07:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.66,0:07:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,A massive army of monsters?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.04,0:07:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be Crocodine's Furfang Legion!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.88,0:07:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,They're launching an all-out attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.76,0:07:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What is all that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.80,0:07:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Dark Army's Furfang Legion!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.76,0:07:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The Furfang Legion?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.89,0:07:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,An army of monsters this size\Nhas never appeared before!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.35,0:07:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Crocodine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.40,0:07:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Go forth! Wipe out Romos Castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.11,0:07:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocodine...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.32,0:07:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.53,0:07:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He's headed for the castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.00,0:08:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai, wait! Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.22,0:08:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.47,0:08:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.22,0:08:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good! The enemy army\Nis overwhelming! We can't hold them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.14,0:08:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Our only option is\Nto help you escape, Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.31,0:08:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot abandon my people and flee!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.40,0:08:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,A king's desertion is the same as defeat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.82,0:08:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I may be old and weak,\Nbut I will not turn tail and run!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.37,0:08:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We must fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.83,0:08:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We must hold out hope until the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.41,0:08:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The gods offer no miracles\Nto those who retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.34,0:08:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Who goes there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.09,0:08:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Legion Commander of\Nthe Furfang Legion of the Dark Army...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.55,0:08:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocodine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.30,0:09:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.39,0:09:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,King Romos, I have no interest\Nin your pathetic life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.15,0:09:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But I need you as bait\Nto lure out my target!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.03,0:09:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to go after Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.87,0:09:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.62,0:09:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you see Crocodine's eye?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.12,0:09:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He intends to kill Dai for revenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.46,0:09:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to help!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.75,0:09:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Count us out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.84,0:09:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.13,0:09:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the point in fighting someone\Nyou know you can't beat?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.97,0:09:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no greater treasure\Nthan one's own life after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.80,0:09:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I can agree to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.31,0:09:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop goofing around! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.31,0:09:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But Crocodine's really strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.69,0:09:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be like just going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.82,0:09:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we have to help!\NDai might get killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.15,0:09:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We all have to work together!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.45,0:10:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.70,0:10:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai's super strong in a pinch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.04,0:10:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He won't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.46,0:10:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.38,0:10:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with you, Popp?!\NAren't you Dai's friend?! His companion?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.30,0:10:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you care about him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.01,0:10:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Lay off me! I never wanted\Nto fight the Dark Army in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.06,0:10:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I never wanted to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.52,0:10:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I know I trained together\Nwith Dai and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.32,0:10:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But he's the reason they keep coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.45,0:10:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to end up\Ndying because of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.87,0:10:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.87,0:10:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.88,0:10:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.34,0:11:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.18,0:11:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you learn anything\Nfrom Master Avan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.52,0:11:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you and Dai\Nwere fighting to avenge him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.85,0:11:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I followed you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.11,0:11:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I joined you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.07,0:11:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.66,0:11:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You disgust me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.04,0:11:37.55,On Top,,0,0,0,,MAGIC BULLET GUN
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.13,0:11:42.55,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}IONAZUN{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}\NEXPLOSION-TYPE SPELL
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.90,0:11:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.78,0:12:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.32,0:12:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.45,0:12:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be... That boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.49,0:12:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are, Dai. I've been waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.58,0:12:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is it really Dai? He's grown up so much!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.50,0:12:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The gods have given me a miracle\Nin the nick of time!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.13,0:12:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight to your heart's content, Crocodine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.05,0:12:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So long as you have that ace\Nup your sleeve, Dai can never win!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.40,0:12:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?! Fight me!\NOtherwise...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.61,0:12:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.41,0:12:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Mera!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.37,0:12:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,A spell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.38,0:13:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In our last battle,\NDai could only use a sword.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.26,0:13:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did he master Mera in only a few days?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.39,0:13:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They say it only takes three days\Nfor someone to change,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.23,0:13:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and he really did!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.40,0:13:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If he continues to grow, he'll become\Nthe greatest threat to the Dark Army!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.66,0:13:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-Dai!\N-Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.62,0:13:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam, cast Behoimi on the king!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.79,0:13:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.25,0:13:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it, Crocodine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.50,0:13:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Throw away your pitiful pride and use it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.84,0:13:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Zaboera, what sort\Nof secret weapon is in that box?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.97,0:13:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It contains that boy's greatest weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.39,0:13:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to use this,\Nbut you leave me no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.36,0:14:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a Magic Cylinder!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.20,0:14:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,A Magic Cylinder?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.07,0:14:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It can contain living creatures!\NYou can bring them in or out with a spell!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.25,0:14:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's like the Magic Bullets\Nthat Master Avan made?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.13,0:14:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! It must contain some sort of backup!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.63,0:14:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Come forth! {\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Derupa!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.23,0:14:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! Grampa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.15,0:14:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Brass is Dai's adoptive parent.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.07,0:14:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a Lump Shaman.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.91,0:14:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If he leaves his island and falls under\Nthe Dark King's Magic Power,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.16,0:14:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,he instantly becomes\Na vanguard for the Dark Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.62,0:15:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Now go, Lump Shaman Brass!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.38,0:15:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.13,0:15:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.13,0:15:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.30,0:15:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my Grampa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.13,0:15:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.84,0:15:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He raised me after I washed up\Non his island! He's not a bad monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.18,0:15:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.85,0:15:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He cannot harm his adoptive parent!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.61,0:15:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no one better to use against Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.28,0:15:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Medapani!{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.49,0:15:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.88,0:15:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.97,0:15:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He had Medapani cast on him\Nso he's confused!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.05,0:15:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.31,0:15:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Sire!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.48,0:16:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go! Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.48,0:16:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Grampa, stop it!\NWhy are you doing this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.28,0:16:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Grampa, wake up!\NDon't you recognize me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.58,0:16:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.06,0:16:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Grampa...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.93,0:16:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Dai...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.90,0:16:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Grampa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.19,0:16:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Merami!{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.20,0:16:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Hadlar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.74,0:16:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.08,0:17:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I have word from my master,\NMystic Bishop Zaboera.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.96,0:17:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He is working with Commander Crocodine\Nof the Furfang Legion to fight Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.80,0:17:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He says victory is at hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.68,0:17:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood. Leave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.93,0:17:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.64,0:17:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Zaboera working together with Crocodine?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.81,0:17:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Curse that Dai.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.44,0:17:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Already he's grown strong enough\Nthat Crocodine can't handle him alone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.82,0:17:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I suppose there's no worry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.49,0:17:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not if Zaboera is lending his wisdom.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.62,0:17:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the Dark Army,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.08,0:17:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}he has the most cunning and cruel mind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.17,0:17:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He cannot be underestimated.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.10,0:18:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Grampa...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.11,0:18:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine, young lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.48,0:18:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Go help Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.74,0:18:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.28,0:18:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.45,0:18:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.20,0:18:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a Merami of my own for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.96,0:18:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.83,0:18:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.88,0:18:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam, you'll hit Grampa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.29,0:18:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But he'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.17,0:18:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Please... He's the only family I've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.26,0:18:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.26,0:18:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,my Grampa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.85,0:18:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Brass, finish...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.60,0:18:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocodine!\NHow can you call yourself a warrior?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.53,0:19:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,After all that talk of pride, I thought\Nyou'd be more honorable than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.53,0:19:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You call yourself the Beast King?!\NDon't make me laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.87,0:19:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.58,0:19:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Using a hostage against a little boy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.58,0:19:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a disgrace of a warrior!\NYou should be ashamed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.08,0:19:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.04,0:19:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Shame on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.29,0:19:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're no warrior!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.55,0:19:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.97,0:19:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A warrior without an achievement\Nis merely a beast with no teeth!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.18,0:19:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Your words mean nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.22,0:19:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already abandoned my pride!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.81,0:19:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He said it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.65,0:19:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Well said, Crocodine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.86,0:19:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,With that attitude,\Nyour victory is assured!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.99,0:19:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Impressive, Master Zaboera.\NTo turn a Legion Commander into a pawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.75,0:19:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Now if Crocodine wins,\Nyour standing is sure to rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.25,0:19:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,After I set all this up,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.84,0:20:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,even a muscle-brained buffoon\Nlike Crocodine can't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.97,0:20:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What can we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.77,0:20:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The Magic Cylinder.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.02,0:20:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.69,0:20:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If we can get that,\Nwe can seal Grampa away again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.23,0:20:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You keep Grampa busy.\NI'll go for the Cylinder.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.45,0:20:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.32,0:20:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Merami!{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.38,0:20:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.05,0:20:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a good plan, but your speed\Nwas halved with the damage from Merale.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.10,0:20:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.35,0:20:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over, Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.36,0:20:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.49,0:21:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't suffer long. I'll end it now...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.78,0:21:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,with this, the Beast King Crocodine's\Nmost powerful attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.09,0:21:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's gathering all of his energy...\Nall of his aura into his right arm!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.14,0:21:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.47,0:21:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Beast King Anguish Blast!{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.27,0:21:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.46,0:21:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Victory is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.19,0:22:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kindness is the magic of kind people{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.19,0:22:25.94,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}yasashisa wa yasashii hito ga tsukaeru mahou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.11,0:22:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then do I have no choice\NBut to just be a normal person?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.11,0:22:32.95,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}jaa boku wa tada no hito de iru shikanaino?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.12,0:22:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not sure{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.12,0:22:36.16,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}doudarou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.46,0:22:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if the place I call home may change{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.46,0:22:44.13,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kaeru basho wa ne kawatte yuku kedo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.30,0:22:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Listen to me, Mother{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.30,0:22:46.67,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}naa kaasan boku wa{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.84,0:22:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will never change those I protect{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.84,0:22:52.81,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mamoru hito wo kaetari shinai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.26,0:22:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder what you'd say{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.26,0:22:57.48,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}anata wa nannte iukana{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.64,0:23:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At times I can be cowardly and small{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.64,0:23:01.69,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tokiyori yowaki de chippoke de{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.86,0:23:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What would you say to me\NAs I hesitate to even hesitate?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.86,0:23:08.15,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mayou koto ni mo mayou boku ni nannte iukana{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.32,0:23:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unlike the today that I sought{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.32,0:23:13.99,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}sagashite ita kyou to chigatte{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.16,0:23:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure you'd laugh at my disappointment{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.16,0:23:19.29,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ochikonnde shimau boku wo warau no darou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.18,0:23:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dai is overwhelmed by\NCrocodine's incredible power.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.60,0:23:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maam is immobilized\Nby the Mystic Bishop Zaboera.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.15,0:23:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The final blow bears down upon them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.19,0:23:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Meanwhile, Popp is far\Nfrom the battlefield.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.99,0:23:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What does Popp feel\Nabout his friends' peril?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.03,0:23:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Next time on{\i0}\NDRAGON QUEST The Adventure of Dai{\i1},{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.37,0:23:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"A Single Shard of Courage"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.25,0:24:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The adventure continues!{\i0}
